@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bgriez(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(tmp + 0.09)) * wp.abs((tmp + 0.75 + v0 + 0.16)))
    v0 = (wp.exp(0.39) * (wp.sin(v1 + 0.74) * 0.97))
    v2 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.42) - (v1 + 0.74 * v1 + 0.35)) - wp.sin(v0))
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.08) * wp.exp(v1 + 0.90)) * 0.74)
    v0 = v2
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.cos(v1 + 0.03) * wp.cos(v2 + 0.82)))
    data[tid] = v0
